sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServe as KServe Router
    participant API as vLLM API Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant GRPC as vllm-tgis-adapter<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Engine as AsyncLLMEngine
    participant Executor as Ray/MP Executor
    participant Worker as HPUWorker
    participant HPU as Intel Gaudi HPU
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,HPU: Flow 1: HTTP Inference Request (OpenAI-compatible)
    Client->>KServe: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Optional TLS, Optional API Key
    KServe->>API: Forward request<br/>8000/TCP
    API->>Engine: Submit inference request<br/>Python IPC
    Engine->>Worker: Schedule on HPU<br/>PyTorch Distributed / MPI
    Worker->>HPU: Execute model forward pass<br/>HPU Runtime
    HPU-->>Worker: Inference result
    Worker-->>Engine: Generated tokens
    Engine-->>API: Streaming tokens
    API-->>KServe: SSE stream or JSON response<br/>Optional TLS
    KServe-->>Client: Response

    Note over Client,HPU: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request (TGIS Adapter)
    Client->>KServe: gRPC GenerationService.Generate
    KServe->>GRPC: Forward gRPC<br/>8033/TCP plaintext
    GRPC->>Engine: Submit via Python API
    Engine->>Worker: Schedule on HPU
    Worker->>HPU: Execute forward pass
    HPU-->>Worker: Result
    Worker-->>Engine: Tokens
    Engine-->>GRPC: Generated response
    GRPC-->>KServe: gRPC response (streaming/unary)
    KServe-->>Client: Response

    Note over Client,HPU: Flow 3: Distributed Multi-Device Inference
    participant Master as MPI Master Worker
    participant Peer as Peer Workers<br/>3022/TCP SSH
    participant RDMA as RDMA Fabric

    Master->>Peer: SSH coordination<br/>3022/TCP SSH keys
    Master->>RDMA: Tensor parallel comm<br/>RDMA/InfiniBand
    Peer->>RDMA: All-reduce operations

    Note over API,HF: Model Loading (startup)
    API->>HF: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS 443, HF_TOKEN Bearer
    HF-->>API: Model artifacts
